615c","tid":1282473,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要飲水<br />\n我要食飯<br />\n我要毛氈<br />\n我有權唔unlock 電話"},{"pid":"1710ee13cbde9f9a8e677cc6109e274997e29003","tid":1282473,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9db9d7e0ed42d821185da3c9a53a3fc94e2914","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"獄中書簡：反送中後的風雲計劃 - 戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714053&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=a97fcff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714053&h=ed885ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714053</a><br />\n<br />\n（二）在452個民選議席中，現在可能仍只有約300個選區有反專制人士參選。民主動力可盡快公佈有哪些選區未有反專制人士參選（俗稱「白區」）。我呼籲，大家慎重考慮在白區參選，讓選民有真正的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7611ba0c9f29e6ff417695441d94c77b37baca21","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b9db9d7e0ed42d821185da3c9a53a3fc94e2914","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"獄中書簡：反送中後的風雲計劃 - 戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714053&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=a97fcff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714053&h=ed885ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714053</a><br />\n<br />\n（二）在452個民選議席中，現在可能仍只有約300個選區有反專制人士參選。民主動力可盡快公佈有哪些選區未有反專制人士參選（俗稱「白區」）。我呼籲，大家慎重考慮在白區參選，讓選民有真正的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"示威者去自己區參選啦！！！！唔好撞區！！！！"},{"pid":"3ac6f1c08c03b223d783a6d9939a394fcfd3546b","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7611ba0c9f29e6ff417695441d94c77b37baca21","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b9db9d7e0ed42d821185da3c9a53a3fc94e2914","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"獄中書簡：反送中後的風雲計劃 - 戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714053&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=a97fcff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714053&h=ed885ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714053</a><br />\n<br />\n（二）在452個民選議席中，現在可能仍只有約300個選區有反專制人士參選。民主動力可盡快公佈有哪些選區未有反專制人士參選（俗稱「白區」）。我呼籲，大家慎重考慮在白區參選，讓選民有真正的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:19:58.000Z","msg":"示威者去自己區參選啦！！！！唔好撞區！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:57:53.000Z","msg":"將支持送中者趕出議會<br />\n<br />\n為了令風雲計劃最終能成功，我相信還有以下幾項工作可以做：（一）在民主動力協調下，大部份選區只有一名反專制人士參選，但還有少數選區協調不成功。我懇切希望大家基於抗爭的大前提，放下個人或組織的考慮，想方法在各區協調出只有一名反專政人士出選，以免建制派漁翁得利。<br />\n<br />\n（二）在452個民選議席中，現在可能仍只有約300個選區有反專制人士參選。民主動力可盡快公佈有哪些選區未有反專制人士參選（俗稱「白區」）。我呼籲，大家慎重考慮在白區參選，讓選民有真正的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n（三）民主派的元老們可考慮在這關鍵時刻重披戰甲，到一些建制派實力強橫的選區參選，以收牽制作用，令其他較年輕的反專制人士有更大機會當選。<br />\n<br />\n（四）在11月區選期間，舉行反專制力量全港性的動員活動（如舉行全港性大遊行或地區性遊行），動員支持反送中的市民積極投票，把所有配合特區政權引入惡法的建制派人士趕出議會。<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月20日<br />\n戴耀廷"},{"pid":"84efa28129d8e944e69cb725ef272ea719d6a8f8","tid":1282473,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bad258ef8bcc0a15590a26438b1c414471ef6ea","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84efa28129d8e944e69cb725ef272ea719d6a8f8","tid":1282473,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"令都更加多人知道，區選和停止拘捕示威者和釋放政治犯的linkage。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選大勝，就唔敢亂告示威者！！！"},{"pid":"addb7163be4fe11ec8454c58038012e3932f450e","tid":1282473,"uid":85909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:13:03.000Z","msg":"我要投票"},{"pid":"b8dfacffcdba02924ab4f73b6a008162eb7b9ac5","tid":1282473,"uid":108245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"今次選舉邊個出黎界票 、叫人含淚、白票等等<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"059878137d258205dd050e45b408ee68390ef24c","tid":1282473,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8dfacffcdba02924ab4f73b6a008162eb7b9ac5","tid":1282473,"uid":108245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"今次選舉邊個出黎界票 、叫人含淚、白票等等<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死全家</span></span>"},"cit